<InnerPage lang={lang} path="/about" title="About — Ostvera" description="Who we are and how we work: turnkey medical equipment supply from China to Russia." heading="About" kicker="Ostvera">
  <p class="lead">Ostvera is an engineering and logistics partner for medical equipment supply from China to Russia. We take on the whole chain — from factory sourcing to commissioning and service.</p>
  <h3>What we do</h3>
  <p>We procure equipment to the client&rsquo;s exact task directly from vetted Chinese manufacturers and ship in-stock items from Russia. We control quality, handle documents, clear customs and deliver.</p>
  <h3>Presence in China</h3>
  <p>We work with ISO 13485 factories. We audit the supplier, inspect the batch and accept samples before shipment &mdash; you don&rsquo;t pay for a pig in a poke.</p>
  <h3>Responsibility on our side</h3>
  <p>One contract, one manager, one area of responsibility: quality, Roszdravnadzor registration, EAEU certification, foreign trade and customs, warranty and service in Russia.</p>
</InnerPage>
